mples\nare computed and illustrate the proposed method's ability to accurately and\nefficiently simulate complex fracture scenarios.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 13 Mar 2022 03:07:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Jun 2022 19:55:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 24 Jun 2022 21:32:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-28"}
